1.0 [2015-05-26]
- Upgrade to manifest_version 2

0.4 [2010-11-07]
- Support for tabs across multiple windows
- Added a new preference to highlight tabs within the currently selected window

0.2 [2010-01-16]

- Tabs can be closed from the popup UI [#2]
- Current tab highlighting [#1]
- Mouseover indication for items in the popup UI [#4]
- Content of the favicon should no longer match filter text [#5]

0.1 [2010-01-14]

- Filter open tabs based on a search string
- Navigate between tabs by selecting the tab entry
